# ============================================
# üìù NOTES
# ============================================

# 1. Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# 2. Never commit .env.local to version control
# 3. Use NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix for variables that need to be exposed to the browser
# 4. Keep sensitive keys (secrets, passwords) on backend only
# 5. Update values for production deployment
# 6. Use environment-specific .env files (.env.development, .env.production)

# ============================================
# üöÄ Quick Setup for Development
# ============================================

# Minimum required variables for local development:
# 1. NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
# 2. NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=ws://localhost:5100
# 3. NEXT_PUBLIC_USE_DEMO_DATA=true (if backend not running)

# For production, you'll need:
# 1. All API URLs pointing to production servers
# 2. Valid Razorpay keys
# 3. Database connection strings
# 4. Email/SMS service credentials
# 5. KYC verification API keys
